# Privacy Policy for DailyWin

**Last updated: April 05, 2025**

DailyWin is a simple, offline-first habit tracker designed to help you win every day.

### We respect your privacy
DailyWin **does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data**.

### Data Storage
- All habits and completion data are stored **locally on your device only** using Android's secure Room database.
- No data is ever sent to any server.
- No analytics, tracking, or advertising IDs are used.
- No account or login is required.

### Permissions
The app requests **no permissions** and has **no internet access**.

### Third-Party Services
- **Motivational quotes** are fetched from the public, free API at https://quotable.io (no user data is sent).
- The app contains **no ads**, **no tracking**, and **no third-party SDKs** that collect data.

### Children's Privacy
DailyWin does not knowingly collect any personal information from children under 13.

### Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this GitHub repository.

### Contact
If you have any questions, feel free to open an issue on this repository or contact the developer at your email (optional).

